              Ages 7-8
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--bc-primary-blue);">YLE Starters (Pre A1)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--bc-dark-gray);">
            A fun first Cambridge exam with colorful tests and stickers. Builds confidence and motivation for young learners.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" style="color: var(--bc-success-green);" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-sm" style="color: var(--muted);">Fun, colorful test format</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" style="color: var(--bc-success-green);" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-sm" style="color: var(--muted);">Every child receives award</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

