              Ages 12-16
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--bc-primary-blue);">B1 Preliminary for Schools (B1)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--bc-dark-gray);">
            Intermediate level English. Required by many Spanish universities and highly valued by employers worldwide.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" style="color: var(--bc-success-green);" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
