              Ages 14-17
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--bc-primary-blue);">B2 First for Schools (B2)</h3>
          <p class="text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--bc-dark-gray);">
